info.description: CandidateZip is a Global Leader of Simplified Resume/Job Data Extraction into ATS/CRM for Recruiters. It is cloud-based resume/CV or Job Parser which converts resumes/CV and jobs to standard fields. This extract contact/location, experience, education, salary, skills, and other fields from resumes/CVs.
info.title: CandidateZip Resume/Job Parser

post.description: Parse JD method can be used to parse job description from public url and get fields
Parse JD method can be used to parse job description from base64 file data and get fields

Parse Resume method can be used to parse resume from public url and get fields extracted (Like Contact info,Pesonal Info, 10 level of experience drill down and 5level of education drill down, and 15 skill drill down)
Parse Resume Basic method can be used to parse resume from public url and get some basic fields extracted (Like Contact info, Skill Keywords, Current employer, JobTitle and Highest degree)

Parse Resume Standard method can be used to parse resume from public url and get fields extracted (Like Contact info, Skill Keywords, and 3 level of experience drill down and 2 level of education drill down)

Parse Resume Binary method can be used to parse resume from base64 data get fields extracted (Like Contact info, Pesonal Info, 10 level of experience drill down and 5level of education drill down, and 15 skill drill down)
post.summary: Parse resume detail via file content
